## SLA Targets

| Metric | Target | Measurement |
|--------|--------|-------------|
| Uptime | 99.9% | Monthly |
| p95 latency | < 500ms | Per-endpoint |
| Error rate | < 0.1% | Rolling 1h window |

## Failure Modes & Mitigations

| Failure | Impact | Mitigation |
|---------|--------|------------|
| DB connection lost | Service degraded | Connection pool retry + circuit breaker |
| Upstream API timeout | Feature unavailable | Timeout + fallback response |
| OOM | Pod restart | Memory limits + leak detection |

