## CI/CD Integration

Add to your pipeline (GitHub Actions example):

```yaml
- name: Architecture Check
  run: npx harness-lab enforce

- name: Doc Health Check
  run: npx harness-lab doctor
```

> **Agents:** If `enforce` or `doctor` fail in CI, fix the violations before proceeding. Never skip or disable these checks.

